{"tid":1033742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【等睇老貓整gif】【CCTV片曝光】電單車女乘客無戴頭盔 飛出十幾米當場爆頭慘死","createTime":"2019-02-23T11:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T10:26:21.000Z","uid":54337,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5455e2d977f57f2e9b56e275385d8eaa36e50c1a","tid":1033742,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"【CCTV片曝光】電單車女乘客無戴頭盔 飛出十幾米當場爆頭慘死<br />\n<br />\n（內容新增）無論坐私家車扣上安全帶，或者坐電單車戴上頭盔，都是為了自身安全着想。甘肅白銀市日前發生一宗恐怖車禍，一輛電單車撞上路中心正在掉頭的一輛的士，女乘客就是因為無戴頭盔被飛出電單車外慘死。<br />\n<br />\n事發於周三（20日），當地一個十字路口上，涉事電單車撞上正在路中心掉頭的一輛的士。從閉路電視畫面所見，電單車女乘客被拋出車前10多米，而司機亦拋出至5米外。女乘客頭部着地慘死，而男司機則骨折。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者指，涉事電單車並非一般電單車，而是跑車，出事前曾多次爬頭超越巴士，事故原因應是電單車車速太快。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的士司機則指，自己當時正掉頭，電單車則撞上的士的車尾。據悉，警方目前已介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190223/59285180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190223%2F59285180&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1Lnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=e2f0309e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190223%2F59285180&h=814063d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190223/59285180</a>"},{"pid":"f2ba8310e01d59feb134123bf39b66283f047d1e","tid":1033742,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"飛到二樓咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba420bda578859c58d76fcd554745e4bf32d1a4","tid":1033742,"uid":42787,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f2ba8310e01d59feb134123bf39b66283f047d1e","tid":1033742,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"飛到二樓咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"麥可⋯⋯"},{"p